//
//   - journal_entry       (header)
//   - journal_entry_line  (debit/credit lines)
//   - account             (COA)
//   - period              (open / soft_close / locked per §1.2 of Doc 09)
//   - reversal_reason     (enum-backed, per §1.3)
//
